citations:
    citation-adwd-appendix:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "Appendix"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "A Dance with Dragons appendix — the most extensive listing in the series. Covers: The King at the Wall (Stannis), King of the Isles and the North (Greyjoys), Houses Arryn/Baratheon/Frey/Lannister/Martell/Stark/Tully/Tyrell, the Night's Watch (Jon Snow as 998th Lord Commander), the Wildlings/Free Folk, Beyond the Wall (Bran and the Three-Eyed Crow), Essos sections (Braavos, Old Volantis, Slaver's Bay), the Queen Across the Water (Daenerys and her court in Meereen), and the Sellsword Companies (Golden Company, Windblown, Company of the Cat, Long Lances, Second Sons, Stormcrows)."
